    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-10-21T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-10-21T17:00:00-05:00" n="77"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d77">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Acting <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul at Saloniki</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_KJE1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kehl</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-10-21T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 21, 1916, 5 p. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You may deal informally and unofficially with Provisional authorities if it
                    becomes necessary. Press reports indicate that Provisional authorities claim
                    that you have recognized their government. In view of this statement greatest
                    care and discretion imperative in official and private intercourse with
                    them.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PFL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
